    "chemicalDescription": [
      "sr-Rainbow Trout Oligopeptide-1 sh-Polypeptide-8 is a single chain fusion peptide, produced by fermentation in  E. coli. The starting gene is synthesized by the fusion of the gene from sr-Rainbow Trout Oligopeptide-1 and sh-Polypeptide-8. The fusion peptide contains 139 amino acids which may contain disulfide bonds and/or glycosylation, and consists of the proper sequence of the 20 standard amino acid."
